            "title": "航空燃油價格翻倍！全球航線面臨大幅削減 瑞銀示警未來幾周恐迎「砍班潮」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CkxN0BujFqtu1TmfOyhKVA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/120c8fda2409f517d526ccd1bb62299e\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E7%87%83%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E7%BF%BB%E5%80%8D-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%88%AA%E7%B7%9A%E9%9D%A2%E8%87%A8%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E5%89%8A%E6%B8%9B-%E7%91%9E%E9%8A%80%E7%A4%BA%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E5%B9%BE%E5%91%A8%E6%81%90%E8%BF%8E-%E7%A0%8D%E7%8F%AD%E6%BD%AE-185003708.html",
